      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655648200_18580748194037525_7874501408691915776_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NjIwMjkyMTEwMDc1NjM4Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=45PB5zZn000Q7kNvwH1OkXy&amp;_nc_oc=AdphklNz-378cr2Kng-8TwNgaLRBnL4jzQjsia1r2hRVHPZNc0x029IRCAmFDq93t5k&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=jr3ZbaKOAUoWNykKDjc6og&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxL-XfaPublDXJrFfII9QfNfbe6ad8xiPJ3NpP_C3zccQ&amp;oe=69C9F990" alt="Slide 1 fra @032c" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/653469590_18580748203037525_6938752368556292652_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NjIwMjkyNDUzMTY1MDMyOQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxNi5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=rR-OJjaGBY0Q7kNvwFY1AT8&amp;_nc_oc=AdoHDiTpqoF4i4ihVe4uZHTG__WfIjU8ByM3wi3XsN5tL1U5RwPz6nPq-JRNd3mfEd0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=jr3ZbaKOAUoWNykKDjc6og&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyFjC4V_B1jrlJ384dzJitamZTuOJZ1b8APPgi8uodnXQ&amp;oe=69CA0745" alt="Slide 2 fra @032c" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/654262929_18580748215037525_8278490458996667688_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NjIwMjkyNTIzNjI5MTMxMg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxNi5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=49pjUHMWsU8Q7kNvwGYBIf_&amp;_nc_oc=AdoVotFY8hi96O7dtbqHHa6QO4Qq33sHIZlWullsSfPmVMi-DdNEPg5PgwHKq5p85FE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=jr3ZbaKOAUoWNykKDjc6og&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyCwBA9xgM0YvsqsSP_jwNa1pfMukixH373yRGTEriaiQ&amp;oe=69C9F09F" alt="Slide 3 fra @032c" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/654026406_18580748224037525_6418391150102026017_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NjIwMjkyODEzMDM5OTk1Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxNi5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=G0sC2fmPvDQQ7kNvwE7uDF5&amp;_nc_oc=AdoqQtjoVMiedBkdpNYr14HVeF6J55TKehsqODL6XxMf4rXFKlg2VQpfJ0s6tZOT2jk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=jr3ZbaKOAUoWNykKDjc6og&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxXYDPPc7a7ed0kxp5kvG3kTwe3vdVpq0s66PvT4H4jFA&amp;oe=69CA2001" alt="Slide 4 fra @032c" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (6 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@032c</strong></p><p>My longest creative collaboration has been with our art director @mikemeire , alongside his deputy Tim Giesen. For almost 20 years - since Issue 13, Energy Experimentation - he has played a crucial role in shaping the identity of 032c. I still remember traveling to Cologne to present him  the very first issue, slightly in awe, because he was… Mike Meiré.<br/>
<br/>
But change is necessary. As we reset 032c in multiple ways, we are also confronting new questions around the magazine’s design and aesthetics. At its core, the challenge is both simple and fundamental: what does it mean to publish a magazine in an AI world?<br/>
<br/>
To explore this, we have decided to begin a new chapter with a different art director and team for the years ahead. This brings an extraordinary run with Mike and Tim (@newflower_edition) to a close - though, in true 032c Hotel California fashion (“You can’t check out”), we are already in conversation about a new project together.<br/>
<br/>
We salute Mike and Tim for their remarkable contribution to 032c, with deep gratitude.<br/>
<br/>
Joerg Koch, founder / EIC <br/>
<br/>
Images: <br/>
👀 Mike and me reviewing the very first issue together in Cologne, 2007 <br/>
